Adhesive Blank Labels & Color Coded: Come with peel-off adhesive labels for identification and making your own personable pocket folder. Being 6 different color coded will make them easier to keep track of your parts manual.
Thicker & More Durable! Consist of tear-resistant poly material that is twice as thick as the others. High-end quality allows it stands up to daily use by teachers and students.

Keep Papers Neatly & Fit in Backpack: Ideal organization tool for students or office workers to sort out loose files, and can withstand being shuffled around a backpack without being bent or disfigure.

Widely Use: Use as a slim alternative to a 3-ring binder and can insert your 3-hole punched materials like presentation, reports, paperwork, artworks, and more. Each pocket can easily hold up more than 50 standard letter size paper.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Do you know how schools always ask for the specific color poly folders that you often have trouble finding at your local school supply store? From now on, there is no need to worry about buying these plastic folders with prongs and pockets that meet the school supplies list with our Sooez multicolored two-pocket plastic folders with 3 prongs. This durable file folder can be used as a document organizer, school folder, homework folder, portfolio folder, bill organizer, or for back-to-school supplies.

Product Design: Two-pocket for storing your loose files3 Prongs for inserting 3-hole pouched sheets2 stay-put tabs for preventing the paper from falling out6 adhesive labels that leave no sticky residue Features: Get All of The Documents in One Brad Folder: Each pocket can comfortably hold 50+ sheets of paper which means each plastic folder has no issues holding 100+ sheets of paper. Functional & Practical: These roomy pronged folders with pockets are lightweight and easy to carry, a good choice for the financial officer, teachers, and students. Products Specifications: Color: orange, green, red, yellow, blue, purple Quantity: 6 Pack Thickness: 35C Material: Made of water-resistant & acid-free & tear-resistant poly Size: 9.4"L x 11.6"W, holds US Letter and other smaller items

Heavy Duty Three Prong Folders Sturdy plastic material which is durable, acid-free, recyclable, water-resistant, and tear-resistant. Two multi-side containment pockets are reinforced for long durability. High-end quality allows it stands up to daily use by teachers, high school, and college, or use as plastic folders for kids. Great Alternative to 3-ring Binder With these 3 metal fasteners, you can insert your 3-hole punched materials like presentation, reports, paperwork, artworks, and more. Using this 2-Pocket Folder as a slim, stylish alternative to a 3-ring binder. Warm Notice: To facilitate the insertion of documents, these three holes are designed to be NOT lined up with the prongs. This is not defective. Vibrant Colors & Adhesive Labels Assorted poly pockets with brad folders come in 6 fresh colors - orange, green, red, yellow, blue, and purple folders with pockets. Color code each folder with prongs to help manage your paperwork and create a more organized reference system.Using labels to mark, and identify the contents of plastic file folders quickly and efficiently, such as subjects, months, financial documents, vacation planners, etc.
